OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wed 18 Mar to Fri 27 Mar
OL,6,FSigns are that much of the UK will see
OL,7,Fa period of more settled weather for
OL,8,Fpart of this period at least. Very
OL,9,Fearly on, some wet and windy weather
OL,10,Fis likely across the far northwest but
OL,11,Fthis will be short-lived. It is likely
OL,12,Fto quickly turn more settled
OL,13,Feverywhere, with most places
OL,14,Fpredominantly dry. Temperatures will
OL,15,Ffluctuate between being milder than
OL,16,Faverage to colder than average, so it
OL,17,Fis possible we could see some
OL,18,Fovernight frost and fog, but overall
OL,19,Fby day there should be spells of
OL,20,Fpleasant spring sunshine making it
OL,21,Ffeel fine away from coasts exposed to
OL,22,Fa brisk easterly wind. How long the
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Fsettled conditions last is less
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
OL,24,Fcertain with some signals that showers
OL,25,F/ rain could return later in the
OL,26,Fperiod.
